{"tid":2097754,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"You are not alone and you’ll never walk alone","createTime":"2020-07-07T04:37:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T04:38:30.000Z","uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2dfc084fbbf8050cce350be6c6ed111166b50d57","tid":2097754,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:37:11.000Z","msg":"香港人<br />\n而家未必係最壞時候<br />\n更差嘅將來可能會使我哋陷入最深淵嘅黑暗<br />\n面對各種不確定性同不安可能會令我哋感到無力同絕望<br />\n即使如此 希望大家都唔好放棄<br />\n唔好忘記我嘅點樣由過去走到現在<br />\n唔好放棄最初嘅想法<br />\n同路人 <br />\n請保留呢一份意志<br />\n唔好放棄信念<br />\n未來雖遙遠但廣大<br />\n願大家可以喺廣闊嘅未來相見<br />\n<br />\nYou Are Not Alone and You&rsquo;ll Never Walk Alone"},{"pid":"3ddaa4d0d508f3bd7ca55e79f1887d1cab06a2b8","tid":2097754,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}